### --------------------
### BRANDS
### --------------------

### Create a brand (Admin only)
POST https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brandName": "Nike"
}

###

### Get all brands
GET https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands

###

### Update a brand (Admin only)
PUT https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands/PUT_BRAND_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brandName": "Adidas"
}

###

### Delete a brand (Admin only)
DELETE https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands/PUT_BRAND_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>

---

### --------------------
### PRODUCTS
### --------------------

### Create a product (Admin only)
POST https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/products
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Air Max 270",
  "cost": 150,
  "productImages": ["https://example.com/image.jpg"],
  "description": "Lightweight running shoes",
  "stockStatus": "in-stock",
  "brandId": "PUT_BRAND_ID_HERE"
}

###

### Get all products (Public)
GET https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/products

###

### Get paginated products by brand
GET https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/products/brands/PUT_BRAND_ID_HERE?page=1&limit=10

###

### Delete a product (Admin only)
DELETE https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/products/PUT_PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>

---

### --------------------
### ORDERS
### --------------------

### Create an order (Customer only)
POST https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/orders
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orders": [
    {
      "productId": "PUT_PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get all orders (Admin only)
GET https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/orders
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>

###

### Get single order by ID (Admin only)
GET https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/orders/PUT_ORDER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>

###

### Update order status (Admin only)
PUT https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/orders/PUT_ORDER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingStatus": "shipped"
}
